						<p><strong>Case  studies</strong><br />
						Several case studies are included, some of which are interactive. Any documentation required for the exercises is provided, along with the suggested answers.</p>
						
						<p>Travel counsellors or students who are not yet enrolled in the CTC program may obtain enrolment forms from ACTA or visit <a href="http://acta.ca/education" rel="external" target="_blank" title="citc.ca - This link opens a new window">acta.ca/education</a> and enrol online.</p>

