							<p>Read or order free copies of the publications online at
								<a href="/travelling/publications" target="_blank" title="This link opens a new window">travel.gc.ca/publications</a>.</p>
							
						<p><strong>Passport applications</strong> <br />
						</p>
						<p>Passport application forms can  be downloaded  from the <a href="http://www.passeportcanada.gc.ca/info/form.aspx"
							rel="external" target="_blank" title="This link opens a new window">Passport Program</a> website or obtained from any Passport Program office, Canada Post outlet, Service Canada Centre or Canadian government office  abroad.</p>
						<p>Requests for bulk application forms must be  placed through the Passport Program online 
							<a href="http://www.canadapost.ca/tools/docp/passport/bin/organization-e.html" rel="external" target="_blank">order form</a>.</p>
