				<h2>Informing your clients</h2>
				<div class="cntnt" id="clients">
						<p>You meet travellers as they are just beginning to plan their trip. At this stage,
							you can really make a difference by ensuring that they are well informed. The Government of Canada provides you with a reliable source of information on:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Security and safety conditions in foreign countries</li>
							<li>Entry requirements</li>
							<li>Health issues</li>
							<li>Social and political situations</li>
						</ul>
						<p>All of this information is available to you at no cost, at the click of a mouse, at <a href="http://travel.gc.ca" target="_blank" title="This link opens a new window">travel.gc.ca</a>.</p>
						
									
